# ambiguity — TypeScript implementation

## Location
`ts/src/` — canonical npm distribution (`ambiguity-analyzer`)

## Key files
- `containers.ts` — verb taxonomy + keyword map + acronym registry
- `parser.ts` — regex token extraction
- `scoring.ts` — ambiguity score (0-10) formula
- `advisory.ts` — priority-ordered advisory rules
- `bridges.ts` — UDL envelope schema and wrapper

## Quality
```bash
cd ts && npm run quality  # biome lint + vitest + tsc --noEmit
```

## Conventions
- No LLM calls — all regex + dict + arithmetic
- Zod schemas for structured output (UDL envelope)
- Mirror src/ambiguity/ patterns exactly
